definitions.definition: ( astronomy ) A constellation of the zodiac supposedly shaped like a centaur who is an archer . It contains the stars Kaus Australis and Nunki .
( astrology ) The zodiac sign for the archer , ruled by Jupiter and covering November 23 - December 21 ( tropical astrology ) or December 16 - January 14 ( sidereal astrology ).
